HEADWORD: nympha
<hw>nym"pha</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Nymphae</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L. See <er>Nymph</er> a
goddess.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Same as
