<p><sn>2.</sn> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Two folds of
mucous membrane, within the labia, at the opening of the
vulva.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nymphaea</ent>⟦br⟧
